WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 18]

02:50.320 --> 02:51.320
Qi?

02:52.160 --> 02:53.130
Qi!

02:56.610 --> 02:57.650
Qi!

03:09.400 --> 03:11.020
Since you miss him so much,

03:11.090 --> 03:12.930
why don't you let him out from under the tree?

03:14.310 --> 03:15.870
Since when did you, the Master of Bright Moon,

03:15.870 --> 03:17.450
start to play tricks like this?

03:17.500 --> 03:19.780
I'm here only to verify one thing.

03:20.570 --> 03:22.400
Last night, I sensed some spiritual presence

03:23.070 --> 03:24.880
within this Emotion Tree.

03:25.250 --> 03:26.800
After we broke loose from the Emotion Tree,

03:26.820 --> 03:29.190
that spiritual presence took shape and attacked me and Bai Shuo.

03:30.050 --> 03:31.570
Its demon aura

03:31.690 --> 03:34.660
is pretty similar to that of Qi, the person

03:34.690 --> 03:35.600
I transformed into

03:37.380 --> 03:38.630
in Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

03:41.520 --> 03:43.120
I was not sure, actually.

03:43.820 --> 03:45.829
But judging from your expression, Master Chang,

03:46.100 --> 03:47.030
I guess

03:47.390 --> 03:49.070
the person buried under the tree

03:49.480 --> 03:51.100
is your lover,

03:51.670 --> 03:52.910
Qi. Am I right?

03:57.630 --> 03:59.070
Can't believe he showed up...

04:01.700 --> 04:02.640
That's right.

04:02.990 --> 04:03.940
We've been worlds apart for 800 years—

04:04.300 --> 04:05.970
one living, one gone.

04:06.560 --> 04:07.600
Now, few people

04:07.630 --> 04:09.280
in this world know that

04:09.280 --> 04:10.590
we were once in love.

04:10.930 --> 04:11.990
Didn't expect

04:12.130 --> 04:14.010
you to know it too, Master Fan.

04:14.610 --> 04:16.200
It was just a coincidence.

04:16.570 --> 04:18.730
Master Fan, you once played Qi.

04:19.360 --> 04:21.560
But Qi was not as lucky as you

04:22.650 --> 04:24.100
to have his beloved one

04:24.160 --> 04:26.090
by his side

04:26.120 --> 04:28.230
and protect her forever.

04:28.460 --> 04:30.630
You came to ask for the Weak Water Stone

04:30.790 --> 04:32.450
for Ms. Bai, right?

04:33.180 --> 04:34.390
You're smart, Master Chang.

04:34.659 --> 04:35.980
Nope,

04:37.330 --> 04:39.190
I've just seen what people in love look like.

04:39.800 --> 04:42.060
I'm familiar with the way

04:42.530 --> 04:43.820
you look at Ms. Bai.

04:45.200 --> 04:46.450
But what a pity...

04:47.250 --> 04:48.350
What?

04:49.240 --> 04:50.860
What on earth happened back then

04:51.230 --> 04:53.390
that left Qi buried deep under the tree?

04:54.050 --> 04:55.630
The Emotion Tree withered?

04:55.659 --> 04:56.630
Why?

04:56.659 --> 04:58.060
Ms. Bai, you know what?

04:58.159 --> 04:59.960
Under the root of the Emotion Tree

05:00.170 --> 05:02.610
once buried the Weak Water Stone.

05:02.640 --> 05:03.740
The Weak Water Stone

05:03.770 --> 05:05.140
is a treasure

05:05.310 --> 05:07.440
forged by the Fox Clan ancestors with the power of true love.

05:07.460 --> 05:08.590
Wherever it is,

05:08.610 --> 05:10.500
the spiritual power abounds like an endless flow.

05:10.740 --> 05:12.380
After that battle 1,000 years ago,

05:12.410 --> 05:13.770
the Fox Clan started to fall into decline.

05:13.790 --> 05:15.080
My brother and I,

05:15.110 --> 05:16.800
along with our Master, had been struggling

05:17.100 --> 05:18.190
for years

05:18.550 --> 05:20.960
until we finally got a chance to bring the Fox Clan back to prosperity.

05:20.980 --> 05:22.230
But 800 years ago,

05:22.250 --> 05:23.780
the Weak Water Stone suddenly went missing.

05:26.160 --> 05:27.640
When did that happen?

05:27.690 --> 05:28.890
Guess it was last night.

05:29.770 --> 05:30.770
Early this morning,

05:30.790 --> 05:31.940
I brought the young foxes here

05:32.500 --> 05:35.170
and saw all the leaves of the Emotion Tree scattered on the ground.

05:35.420 --> 05:36.540
I checked out with my spiritual power

05:36.659 --> 05:38.810
[Qi, Demon Race, Fox Attendant]

05:37.020 --> 05:37.909
and found nothing

05:37.970 --> 05:38.880
down there.

05:39.220 --> 05:40.250
Then what are we waiting for?

05:40.840 --> 05:42.210
Let's shut down the mountain entrance

05:42.240 --> 05:43.409
and block all access!

05:43.430 --> 05:44.670
No matter who stole it,

05:44.700 --> 05:46.700
we must try to find the Weak Water Stone by all means!

05:46.720 --> 05:47.530
No.

05:48.540 --> 05:49.820
All the races and clans around

05:49.850 --> 05:51.530
are keeping an eye on the Jingyou Mountain, ready to move.

05:51.550 --> 05:53.140
A high-profile search

05:53.190 --> 05:54.880
will alert others to the Emotion Tree's anomaly,

05:54.900 --> 05:56.330
and they'll surely take the chance to cause trouble.

05:57.240 --> 05:59.460
Our Fox Clan went through a lot and just got back to our feet.

05:59.490 --> 06:00.750
We can't stand another blow.

06:00.780 --> 06:01.780
But if we just

06:01.840 --> 06:03.450
see the Emotion Tree wither without doing anything,

06:03.480 --> 06:05.350
the descendants of our clan will not be able to grow emotional veins

06:05.370 --> 06:06.810
and cultivate curses.

06:06.830 --> 06:07.990
At this rate,

06:08.170 --> 06:09.690
the Jingyou Mountain will still be in trouble.

06:09.760 --> 06:11.080
So none of them is feasible?

06:11.100 --> 06:12.410
What on earth should we do?

06:15.020 --> 06:16.610
Fill it with my life.

06:18.470 --> 06:19.400
What do you mean?

06:21.210 --> 06:23.990
The Weak Water Stone just provided nutrients of spiritual power.

06:24.010 --> 06:26.020
As long as we keep offering the Emotion Tree spiritual power,

06:26.040 --> 06:27.310
it will stop withering.

06:27.690 --> 06:30.290
Now in the Fox Clan, I'm the one with the greatest spiritual power.

06:30.990 --> 06:32.490
With the Weak Water Stone gone,

06:32.780 --> 06:33.930
I'll support it with my life.

06:34.850 --> 06:35.730
Wu,

06:35.750 --> 06:36.900
stop talking nonsense.

06:36.930 --> 06:37.900
You're the Master of Jingyou Mountain.

06:37.920 --> 06:39.510
Just because I'm the Master,

06:39.540 --> 06:41.659
I must solve this case.

06:42.130 --> 06:43.400
As you can see,

06:43.430 --> 06:45.190
those clan members

06:45.230 --> 06:47.790
just won't let go of what my sister did back then

06:47.810 --> 06:49.980
as if the one who wiped out their families was not Rong Xian,

06:50.000 --> 06:51.610
but my sister.

06:51.640 --> 06:53.640
But you still can't risk your life out of rage.

06:53.659 --> 06:55.020
It's not out of rage.

06:56.200 --> 06:57.280
I'm just tired.

06:59.900 --> 07:00.780
Qi,

07:01.140 --> 07:02.200
to them,

07:02.600 --> 07:05.420
all the toil and hard work we've done for the Fox Clan over the years

07:05.920 --> 07:07.160
is no more than

07:07.180 --> 07:09.230
the atonement we're supposed to make.

07:10.400 --> 07:12.930
I've had enough of them badmouthing me behind my back

07:12.960 --> 07:14.750
and me having to endure their attitudes.

07:15.880 --> 07:17.860
Let me pay with my life,

07:18.160 --> 07:19.450
and then they'll know that

07:19.870 --> 07:22.270
my sister never owed them anything.

07:23.550 --> 07:24.920
What Rong Xian did back then

07:25.530 --> 07:26.690
was a tragedy.

07:27.700 --> 07:29.100
It's totally reasonable for the Fox Clan

07:29.450 --> 07:30.850
to hate Rong Xian.

07:31.310 --> 07:32.700
But why did they blame Ling Long

07:33.150 --> 07:34.690
and even take it out on you?

07:35.680 --> 07:37.330
Don't you know that

07:37.860 --> 07:41.010
the malice in our hearts is the most poisonous thing in the world?

07:41.890 --> 07:43.890
When Ling Long was still the Saintess,

07:43.909 --> 07:45.850
those people were all fawning

07:45.870 --> 07:47.260
and groveling.

07:47.380 --> 07:49.270
But once everything fell,

07:49.560 --> 07:52.120
my sister became the sinner condemned by everyone.

07:52.960 --> 07:54.450
Ling Long fell in love with Rong Xian.

07:55.010 --> 07:57.090
It was nothing wrong for her to die for true love.

07:57.460 --> 07:59.909
Were it not for the feud between the Fox Clan and Kunlun,

08:00.840 --> 08:03.040
maybe things wouldn't have ended up like that.

08:03.410 --> 08:06.490
Her love became the evidence of stigma in everyone's eyes,

08:06.510 --> 08:08.020
and she suffered endless accusations.

08:08.910 --> 08:09.870
The hatred of the Fox Clan

08:09.890 --> 08:12.520
gave them a reason to direct all their hatred at me.

08:13.380 --> 08:14.910
I should have died

08:14.940 --> 08:16.650
for relief.

08:17.660 --> 08:18.820
But unfortunately,

08:18.970 --> 08:20.400
Qi loved me.

08:20.630 --> 08:21.750
Because of this love,

08:22.500 --> 08:24.420
he was willing to sacrifice his life

08:24.620 --> 08:25.890
to save me.

08:44.390 --> 08:45.350
Qi!

08:52.570 --> 08:53.330
Qi...

08:53.460 --> 08:54.100
Wu,

08:55.450 --> 08:56.760
My biggest regret

08:57.100 --> 08:57.870
is not being able

08:57.870 --> 08:59.460
to see you in that wedding dress.

08:59.590 --> 09:01.270
No, Qi!

09:00.780 --> 09:02.680
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

09:02.930 --> 09:04.280
No, stop!

09:03.010 --> 09:04.930
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

09:05.040 --> 09:06.830
♫My love brought tears♫

09:07.080 --> 09:08.800
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

09:07.720 --> 09:08.530
No!

09:09.220 --> 09:11.050
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

09:10.420 --> 09:11.770
No!

09:11.260 --> 09:12.680
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

09:12.890 --> 09:14.510
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

09:14.850 --> 09:16.860
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

09:15.240 --> 09:16.780
No!

09:17.060 --> 09:18.680
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

09:18.920 --> 09:20.700
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

09:19.840 --> 09:20.990
Qi...

09:20.970 --> 09:22.990
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

09:23.290 --> 09:24.850
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

09:24.990 --> 09:26.040
Qi...

09:25.190 --> 09:27.080
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

09:27.350 --> 09:29.350
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

09:29.650 --> 09:31.150
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

09:31.350 --> 09:33.810
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

09:35.130 --> 09:36.330
After Qi died,

09:36.520 --> 09:38.820
the Master was depressed for a really long time.

09:39.580 --> 09:40.570
With my brother gone,

09:40.820 --> 09:43.060
I had to work harder to take care of the Fox Clan

09:43.360 --> 09:45.240
so that his life wouldn't be sacrificed for nothing.

09:46.040 --> 09:47.440
With the nutrients,

09:47.480 --> 09:49.310
the Emotion Tree was back to being lush and thriving.

09:49.480 --> 09:50.450
Just like that,

09:50.680 --> 09:52.130
hundreds of years flew by.

09:53.090 --> 09:55.190
We thought everything would be fine.

09:55.350 --> 09:56.820
But my brother's spiritual power

09:57.140 --> 09:58.690
will be exhausted one day.

09:59.480 --> 10:00.760
That's why

10:00.800 --> 10:02.920
the Emotion Tree began to swallow people

10:02.940 --> 10:04.720
to continue to obtain spiritual power?

10:05.040 --> 10:06.020
At first,

10:06.390 --> 10:08.440
we didn't notice anything unusual.

10:09.330 --> 10:11.150
Not until a few outsiders came

10:12.100 --> 10:13.620
and got swallowed when they

10:13.670 --> 10:14.920
passed by the Emotion Tree

10:14.940 --> 10:16.750
did it occur to the Master.

10:16.780 --> 10:19.380
Qi's body is buried under the Emotion Tree.

10:19.400 --> 10:21.040
Qi was loyal to the Fox Clan and the Master

10:21.070 --> 10:22.340
all his life.

10:22.360 --> 10:24.030
So our clan members are safe.

10:24.250 --> 10:25.790
But outsiders are different.

10:27.070 --> 10:28.800
If someone gets close to the Emotion Tree,

10:28.900 --> 10:31.310
they will be enchanted by the desire for love

10:31.950 --> 10:33.240
and see the people and things they love

10:33.270 --> 10:34.550
in their illusions,

10:34.570 --> 10:35.820
willing to get killed.

10:36.500 --> 10:37.780
You mean

10:38.650 --> 10:40.190
Qi's the one who's hurting people?

10:40.220 --> 10:42.360
The Emotion Tree ending up as such an evil thing

10:42.360 --> 10:43.680
was definitely not my brother's intention.

10:43.710 --> 10:45.470
There must be something fishy behind this.

10:46.560 --> 10:47.420
Ms. Bai,

10:47.920 --> 10:50.110
you once saw my brother in the illusion.

10:50.400 --> 10:51.720
so you should know

10:51.750 --> 10:53.740
how righteous and kind he was.

10:53.760 --> 10:55.960
We grew up together.

10:56.170 --> 10:58.220
I can't summarize everything I know about him in just a few words.

10:59.930 --> 11:01.420
Others may not understand,

11:02.110 --> 11:03.210
but, Ms. Bai,

11:03.500 --> 11:04.890
I believe you can feel it.

11:05.300 --> 11:07.030
I trust Qi.

11:07.290 --> 11:08.530
But now,

11:08.560 --> 11:10.170
it's also true that

11:10.190 --> 11:11.480
the Emotion Tree swallows people.

11:11.500 --> 11:12.380
So,

11:12.690 --> 11:15.060
Ms. Bai, I hope you can get to the bottom of this case.

11:15.080 --> 11:17.140
Since you could make Rong Xian's obsession from 1,000 years ago disappear,

11:17.220 --> 11:18.980
then you can definitely dispel

11:19.040 --> 11:20.160
my brother's lingering soul.

11:20.720 --> 11:23.670
I'll do whatever it takes to repay you, Ms. Bai.

11:23.930 --> 11:24.960
Anything you ask for.

11:29.800 --> 11:30.850
No way.

11:32.950 --> 11:34.850
After Qi sacrificed his life to the Emotion Tree,

11:35.010 --> 11:36.820
his soul has never appeared.

11:37.160 --> 11:38.640
His sudden appearance last night

11:38.670 --> 11:40.530
must have something to do with Ms. Bai's blood.

11:40.560 --> 11:41.960
It must be the power of the Contemplation Stone!

11:41.980 --> 11:43.030
It was a miracle!

11:44.180 --> 11:45.000
Fan Yue,

11:45.210 --> 11:46.830
I'm not fighting for that stone.

11:46.860 --> 11:48.230
Neither do I want to be your enemy.

11:48.440 --> 11:50.700
I really just want to see Qi once again.

11:51.450 --> 11:52.570
I promise

11:52.590 --> 11:54.670
I won't hurt Ms. Bai.

11:54.700 --> 11:56.530
I just need a little bit of her blood.

11:56.550 --> 11:57.640
As I said before,

11:57.670 --> 11:58.750
no way.

11:59.530 --> 12:01.810
You promised to give me the Weak Water Stone in three days,

12:02.550 --> 12:03.790
yet you failed me.

12:04.070 --> 12:05.880
Since you and Qi were innocent,

12:05.900 --> 12:06.970
I didn't hold you accountable.

12:07.100 --> 12:08.430
But don't go too far.

12:09.370 --> 12:11.700
But as sensible as you are, Master Fan,

12:12.280 --> 12:14.880
can't you have any mercy on the two of us?

12:15.520 --> 12:17.270
The illusion Rong Xian left

12:17.450 --> 12:19.690
means the fate between you and us.

12:19.710 --> 12:21.510
I beg you.

12:22.820 --> 12:24.010
I'll help you.

12:27.110 --> 12:28.110
Ms. Bai.

12:28.130 --> 12:30.210
Bai Shuo, do you have to go against me?

12:30.280 --> 12:31.930
You can't even take care of yourself right now.

12:31.960 --> 12:33.110
How can you help others?

12:33.140 --> 12:34.530
I know what I'm saying.

12:35.150 --> 12:36.670
And I'm fully aware of what I'm doing.

12:37.270 --> 12:39.000
Master Chang was right.

12:39.180 --> 12:41.330
You and I should know Qi best.

12:41.870 --> 12:43.590
He won't hurt anyone.

12:45.270 --> 12:47.560
Do you remember Ling Long's last words?

12:48.770 --> 12:51.100
She wanted Wu to stay away from the fight between Eternals and demons,

12:51.130 --> 12:52.300
take care of herself,

12:52.500 --> 12:54.330
and live a free and peaceful life.

12:54.620 --> 12:56.450
But what does it have to do with you?

12:56.600 --> 12:58.210
This is Ling Long's wish.

12:59.290 --> 13:00.590
But

13:01.000 --> 13:02.360
for the Fox Clan,

13:02.380 --> 13:03.830
Wu gave up freedom

13:04.960 --> 13:06.630
and chose responsibility.

13:06.660 --> 13:08.420
If I can't help Wu this time,

13:08.440 --> 13:09.890
I'll feel guilty.

13:10.910 --> 13:12.600
You didn't kill those foxes.

13:12.690 --> 13:14.360
And Qi's death was also not your fault.

13:14.740 --> 13:16.300
Why would you feel guilty?

13:16.330 --> 13:18.410
But I can do her a favor now.

13:18.690 --> 13:20.030
Do you want me to turn a blind eye?

13:20.050 --> 13:21.440
But you're no more than a human!

13:21.470 --> 13:23.510
Yeah, a human who got the Contemplation Stone by luck.

13:35.240 --> 13:36.030
Master Chang,

13:37.190 --> 13:39.810
I learned about you from Ling Long.

13:39.840 --> 13:41.930
I also felt the warmth Ling Long gave me by holding my hand

13:42.570 --> 13:44.650
and taking care of me as her little sister.

13:45.680 --> 13:46.870
You may not know that

13:47.610 --> 13:49.020
I used to have an elder sister too.

13:49.740 --> 13:51.490
She's not with me now.

13:52.040 --> 13:53.150
I believe

13:53.200 --> 13:54.560
if Ling Long were still alive,

13:54.900 --> 13:56.520
if my sister were still with me,

13:56.960 --> 13:58.910
they would never see their sisters

13:59.150 --> 14:00.880
suffer the agony of being separated

14:01.400 --> 14:02.820
from their beloved ones

14:03.450 --> 14:04.670
without doing anything.

14:05.360 --> 14:07.390
The tragedy from a thousand years ago should have ended long ago.

14:07.860 --> 14:08.900
I'm willing to help you.

14:09.690 --> 14:10.570
Ms. Bai...

14:10.600 --> 14:11.480
Excuse me, Master Chang.

14:13.260 --> 14:14.860
We need to talk alone.

14:30.630 --> 14:31.430
Come out.

14:32.640 --> 14:34.290
How much longer are you going to hide from me?

14:37.820 --> 14:39.340
N-No, I'm not hiding.

14:39.480 --> 14:40.340
Fine.

14:40.610 --> 14:42.660
Bai Shuo entrusted you with a gift from Chang Mei

14:42.690 --> 14:43.630
to me.

14:43.660 --> 14:44.630
Where is it?

14:46.920 --> 14:47.710
I didn't see it.

14:49.670 --> 14:50.880
What a man...

14:50.900 --> 14:53.120
You're really bad at lying.

14:53.210 --> 14:55.060
Are you really going to avoid me

14:55.080 --> 14:56.590
and never talk to me again?

14:59.870 --> 15:00.960
If you don't like Mu Jiu,

15:00.960 --> 15:01.910
why are you going to marry him?

15:01.910 --> 15:02.550
Even if it's fake,

15:02.550 --> 15:03.200
it's going way too far.

15:03.220 --> 15:03.870
I like him...

15:03.890 --> 15:05.090
I like him...

15:19.670 --> 15:21.020
But it's just a tiny bit of love

15:22.230 --> 15:23.880
that's just beginning to sprout.

15:24.680 --> 15:27.190
It's too subtle to be caught even by myself.

15:27.820 --> 15:29.600
But when you fought him,

15:30.170 --> 15:31.590
I felt nervous

15:31.930 --> 15:33.340
and worried.

15:34.530 --> 15:36.510
Only then did I realize

15:37.890 --> 15:39.410
that I actually liked him.

15:40.020 --> 15:41.000
You like him.

15:41.000 --> 15:41.910
Then what about me?

15:41.980 --> 15:43.020
What about the Master?

15:43.460 --> 15:45.020
We are still the same as we were.

15:45.270 --> 15:46.470
We're still friends.

15:48.050 --> 15:49.910
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

15:49.440 --> 15:52.090
The world is not just about the romantic love between men and women.

15:50.560 --> 15:52.390
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

15:52.110 --> 15:54.390
The bond between you, the Master, and me

15:52.910 --> 15:55.790
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

15:54.420 --> 15:55.770
is friendship.

15:56.190 --> 15:59.760
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

15:56.980 --> 15:58.200
Cang Shan,

15:58.570 --> 15:59.880
it's no more than friendship.

15:59.930 --> 16:03.190
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

16:03.880 --> 16:06.200
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

16:05.970 --> 16:07.020
Now,

16:06.930 --> 16:08.260
♫Time after time♫

16:07.950 --> 16:10.120
can you give me that wedding dress?

16:09.020 --> 16:13.820
♫Oh, melancholy♫

16:17.290 --> 16:18.580
No need to say anything.

16:18.740 --> 16:19.470
I will never

16:19.640 --> 16:20.760
say yes to this matter.

16:23.500 --> 16:25.740
Do you remember why I wanted to become a god

16:25.810 --> 16:27.400
when we were back in Ning'an City?

16:28.470 --> 16:30.420
When I was still a kid,

16:30.580 --> 16:32.520
a great immortal saved me and my sister.

16:33.220 --> 16:35.150
We survived all thanks to him.

16:35.400 --> 16:37.230
He said a deity's lifespan is really long,

16:37.440 --> 16:38.910
and he wouldn't stick around to wait for me to repay him.

16:39.150 --> 16:40.910
So I wanted to become a god

16:41.210 --> 16:42.910
and fulfill my promise.

16:43.630 --> 16:44.950
Now, you're going to sacrifice your life

16:45.230 --> 16:46.650
before you fulfill it.

16:47.160 --> 16:49.040
Looks like you've already forgotten

16:49.060 --> 16:50.220
about your benefactor's words, huh?

16:50.340 --> 16:51.940
I know you're worried about me.

16:52.600 --> 16:54.320
The Weak Water Stone is missing.

16:54.340 --> 16:55.960
I don't know how long

16:56.460 --> 16:58.160
the Contemplation Stone can last in my body.

16:58.580 --> 17:00.480
You ignored your own safety

17:00.500 --> 17:01.890
and tried to save me first.

17:02.720 --> 17:03.600
Fan Yue,

17:04.130 --> 17:05.310
I'm really grateful.

17:05.609 --> 17:06.329
Thank you.

17:08.670 --> 17:10.690
But I also have something I want to do.

17:10.880 --> 17:11.849
Chang Mei

17:12.170 --> 17:14.079
is an old sly fox who has lived for 1000 years.

17:14.290 --> 17:15.880
You don't know

17:15.910 --> 17:16.859
if she told the truth today.

17:17.440 --> 17:18.430
Qi's death

17:18.460 --> 17:20.630
is just a story pieced from her words.

17:20.880 --> 17:22.000
Don't you think

17:22.000 --> 17:23.520
things are fishy and suspicious about it?

17:23.569 --> 17:24.220
Fine.

17:24.560 --> 17:26.160
What she is hiding has nothing to do with me.

17:26.920 --> 17:28.720
I don't want to meddle in the Fox Clan's crisis.

17:29.030 --> 17:30.030
Taking a few drops of your blood

17:30.030 --> 17:31.570
doesn't sound like a big deal.

17:31.730 --> 17:33.360
But what if she's up to something else?

17:33.610 --> 17:34.690
I know.

17:35.260 --> 17:37.580
But I also want to find out the secret behind the Emotion Tree.

17:37.830 --> 17:39.290
If I shrink from taking any risk

17:39.310 --> 17:40.550
after knowing

17:40.580 --> 17:41.910
my days are numbered

17:41.930 --> 17:43.310
just to survive,

17:43.330 --> 17:44.440
it'll not only let down

17:44.560 --> 17:46.630
my benefactor but also myself.

17:48.970 --> 17:50.160
You should know

17:50.730 --> 17:52.240
how it feels.

17:52.570 --> 17:53.480
The Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal

17:53.500 --> 17:55.330
has been on you for quite a while.

17:54.060 --> 17:57.130
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

17:55.880 --> 17:57.990
Did those life-and-death crises

17:57.430 --> 18:00.630
♫When my star falls only for you♫

17:58.250 --> 17:59.530
ever freak you out?

17:59.550 --> 18:00.270
That's because...

18:00.270 --> 18:01.440
Because you're strong.

18:01.380 --> 18:03.140
♫When the heavens fall♫

18:02.710 --> 18:04.240
You have full confidence in yourself.

18:03.580 --> 18:08.630
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

18:05.080 --> 18:06.640
But no one is born strong.

18:06.670 --> 18:08.460
Not to mention that I'm a human.

18:08.840 --> 18:10.460
If I don't train myself

18:08.930 --> 18:11.850
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

18:10.660 --> 18:12.500
and overcome every difficulty,

18:12.170 --> 18:16.310
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

18:12.520 --> 18:14.910
I will never become stronger.

18:15.710 --> 18:16.580
So,

18:16.900 --> 18:25.800
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

18:17.030 --> 18:19.200
you know Chang Mei's probably lying,

18:19.600 --> 18:21.040
yet you still want to get yourself involved?

18:22.290 --> 18:22.960
Yes.

18:25.850 --> 18:27.050
Besides,

18:27.720 --> 18:28.910
I have you with me.

18:28.930 --> 18:29.860
Am I right?

18:38.870 --> 18:39.760
Master,

18:40.450 --> 18:42.040
we deceived Ms. Bai.

18:42.570 --> 18:44.270
If the Master of Bright Moon finds out,

18:44.650 --> 18:46.160
he won't let it go, I'm afraid.

18:46.180 --> 18:47.830
I didn't lie to her.

18:48.390 --> 18:51.300
Qi did sacrifice his life to the Emotion Tree.

18:51.400 --> 18:53.530
The feelings between Qi and me

18:53.820 --> 18:55.150
were also real.

18:55.380 --> 18:56.790
But the Weak Water Stone wasn't lost.

18:56.820 --> 18:57.350
It's right in...

18:57.350 --> 18:58.070
Shut up!

18:59.810 --> 19:01.350
When my brother died,

19:02.010 --> 19:03.340
he asked me to protect you, Master.

19:04.250 --> 19:05.310
All these years,

19:05.490 --> 19:06.790
in my heart,

19:06.910 --> 19:08.910
you are like my sister,

19:10.330 --> 19:11.740
my sister-in-law.

19:18.400 --> 19:19.490
I know

19:20.020 --> 19:21.690
everything you've done

19:21.720 --> 19:23.120
is for the Fox Clan.

19:23.370 --> 19:25.570
But Qi is dead!

19:26.540 --> 19:29.090
The one inside the Emotion Tree now is an evil monster!

19:29.780 --> 19:31.010
So what?

19:31.160 --> 19:33.960
Ms. Bai's blood has got the aura of the Contemplation Stone.

19:33.990 --> 19:35.270
If we use her blood to nourish it,

19:35.300 --> 19:37.300
that evil monster might grow stronger!

19:37.420 --> 19:38.950
If he is no longer Qi,

19:38.980 --> 19:39.750
letting him out

19:39.790 --> 19:42.110
will put the entire Fox Clan in danger!

19:42.490 --> 19:43.810
What if my original purpose

19:46.460 --> 19:48.680
was never to let Qi out?

19:54.150 --> 19:56.040
Last time when the Emotion Tree was dying,

19:57.020 --> 19:58.830
Qi sacrificed all his cultivation

19:58.860 --> 20:00.400
to the Emotion Tree.

20:00.970 --> 20:02.010
This time,

20:02.730 --> 20:04.560
I once wanted to do the same thing by myself,

20:06.800 --> 20:08.250
But Fan Yue came.

20:08.520 --> 20:10.790
I was wondering that, with his powerful spiritual energy,

20:10.890 --> 20:12.560
there could be a silver lining.

20:13.820 --> 20:15.470
Now we've got a chance, right?

20:17.360 --> 20:18.260
Master,

20:18.540 --> 20:20.410
are you going to kill Ms. Bai?

20:20.700 --> 20:23.380
Today, Fan Yue's words made me realize that

20:24.500 --> 20:25.840
the Weak Water Stone

20:25.900 --> 20:27.550
is no more than the Fox Clan's treasure,

20:27.680 --> 20:31.470
yet the Contemplation Stone is the real divine stone.

20:31.570 --> 20:33.260
If we bury Bai Shuo

20:33.820 --> 20:35.580
under the Emotion Tree,

20:36.130 --> 20:38.320
then the Tree

20:38.540 --> 20:40.710
will thrive forever and ever.

20:41.130 --> 20:42.680
Master, you...

20:43.270 --> 20:45.270
This is wild and unrealistic!

20:45.300 --> 20:46.820
Before we talk about whether it works,

20:46.840 --> 20:48.000
even if we do it,

20:48.820 --> 20:51.060
the Master of Bright Moon will never agree.

20:52.670 --> 20:53.990
At this point,

20:54.920 --> 20:56.820
I have no other choice.

20:58.450 --> 20:59.270
Ba,

21:00.690 --> 21:03.040
I have to carry this out.

21:05.080 --> 21:06.990
Let go of me! Let go!

21:07.630 --> 21:10.300
Am I a prisoner or a groom?

21:11.000 --> 21:12.200
Let go of me!

21:13.030 --> 21:14.310
What did I do

21:14.340 --> 21:15.580
to deserve to be watched over like this?

21:15.600 --> 21:17.500
Do you think I want to watch you?

21:17.740 --> 21:19.270
It's all your Auntie's order.

21:19.940 --> 21:21.180
Auntie...

21:21.200 --> 21:22.370
It's Auntie again!

21:23.320 --> 21:24.560
I lost my parents when I was young.

21:24.590 --> 21:25.840
I thought I could lead a carefree life.

21:25.860 --> 21:26.880
But, oh my God,

21:26.910 --> 21:28.200
I've still got such an annoying Auntie!

21:28.530 --> 21:29.840
I'm not even 20,

21:29.860 --> 21:30.590
yet half of my life

21:30.590 --> 21:32.000
has been spent being treated like a prisoner.

21:33.350 --> 21:34.070
I think

21:34.100 --> 21:36.130
I was just born into captivity,

21:36.150 --> 21:37.230
unable to escape.

21:37.260 --> 21:38.880
What a worthless life.

21:38.900 --> 21:39.710
Gosh.

21:41.050 --> 21:42.530
You should be grateful.

21:42.550 --> 21:43.500
In the Fox Clan,

21:43.530 --> 21:45.310
we're either family or related in some way.

21:45.330 --> 21:46.160
Let's not talk about the others.

21:46.190 --> 21:47.600
There are a dozen orphans

21:47.620 --> 21:49.060
in your generation.

21:49.390 --> 21:50.950
But only you

21:50.970 --> 21:51.840
were picked by the Master

21:51.870 --> 21:52.950
and taken in as her nephew.

21:53.670 --> 21:54.540
Now,

21:54.600 --> 21:56.160
you've hit the jackpot

21:56.200 --> 21:57.770
and are going to succeed as the Master of Jingyou Mountain.

21:57.790 --> 21:58.390
Don't you think

21:58.420 --> 22:00.490
you're so lucky that everyone would envy you?

22:02.460 --> 22:03.810
Succeed as the Master of Jingyou Mountain?

22:04.930 --> 22:06.780
Hasn't the succession ceremony been changed into the wedding?

22:06.810 --> 22:08.050
Why are you still talking about that?

22:12.510 --> 22:13.510
Elder...

22:16.400 --> 22:17.950
Are you

22:18.250 --> 22:20.420
colluding with my Auntie to cheat me?

22:20.740 --> 22:21.820
No!

22:21.840 --> 22:23.320
No more wild guesses.

22:23.350 --> 22:23.970
By the way,

22:24.080 --> 22:25.120
I need to go to the forest

22:25.140 --> 22:26.820
to find those two people from the Cold Spring Palace.

22:26.850 --> 22:27.920
That's it.

22:27.940 --> 22:28.750
I gotta go now.

22:28.780 --> 22:29.730
See you.

22:29.750 --> 22:30.670
Don't go!

22:30.690 --> 22:31.490
Young Master...

22:33.150 --> 22:34.670
Move it to tomorrow?

22:34.690 --> 22:35.800
Why?

22:35.850 --> 22:37.440
Didn't we reach an agreement?

22:37.550 --> 22:39.630
Tian Huo is my good friend.

22:39.650 --> 22:40.540
I shouldn't

22:40.570 --> 22:42.820
miss her wedding no matter what.

22:42.910 --> 22:45.300
I've promised you that I would release Qi

22:45.330 --> 22:46.940
for your reunion,

22:46.970 --> 22:48.300
and I will never go back on my word.

22:48.320 --> 22:50.880
One day earlier or later, there's no big difference.

22:51.700 --> 22:53.480
Ms. Bai, you should also know that

22:53.540 --> 22:55.770
everyone in the clan

22:55.790 --> 22:57.970
will attend their wedding tonight.

22:58.250 --> 23:01.220
The Emotion Tree is really important to the Jingyou Mountain.

23:01.250 --> 23:03.600
If something goes wrong and alerts the others,

23:03.620 --> 23:05.110
it will inevitably cause chaos.

23:05.250 --> 23:06.350
As the Master of Jingyou Mountain,

23:06.370 --> 23:08.310
I've got to maintain peace within our clan.

23:08.330 --> 23:10.490
Hope you can understand.

23:11.010 --> 23:12.600
Does it have to be tonight?

23:12.620 --> 23:13.470
Yes.

23:16.530 --> 23:17.410
Alright.

23:17.520 --> 23:19.310
Since you've asked for it,

23:19.340 --> 23:20.890
I should respect your request.

23:24.450 --> 23:25.220
By the way,

23:25.830 --> 23:27.070
Master Chang,

23:27.090 --> 23:28.930
when is Mu Jiu's birthday?

23:28.960 --> 23:30.090
And how old is he?

23:30.250 --> 23:32.930
He was born in September, and he's not over 20.

23:33.130 --> 23:34.650
Why are you asking this?

23:35.590 --> 23:36.940
I am of the Human Race.

23:36.970 --> 23:39.810
Marriage should always take horoscopes into account.

23:39.940 --> 23:41.570
I'm just curious.

23:41.860 --> 23:42.550
I'm leaving.

23:51.520 --> 23:53.560
Chang Mei deliberately chose today.

23:53.590 --> 23:55.200
There must be a special reason.

23:55.360 --> 23:56.840
What's so special about today?

23:56.860 --> 23:57.990
The first day of the ninth lunar month.

23:58.020 --> 23:59.160
Anything significant?

24:01.020 --> 24:03.850
Chang Mei mentioned that Mu Jiu's birthday is also in the ninth lunar month.

24:04.600 --> 24:06.600
Could it be that she insists on holding the wedding today

24:06.630 --> 24:08.560
because it's Mu Jiu's birthday?

24:09.020 --> 24:10.600
That doesn't quite add up, though.

24:11.420 --> 24:12.580
No need to overthink it.

24:12.880 --> 24:14.360
I'll go with you tonight.

24:14.690 --> 24:15.760
With me there,

24:15.850 --> 24:16.550
nothing will go wrong.

24:18.910 --> 24:19.840
I'll go too.

24:20.090 --> 24:21.550
You stay here for the wedding.

24:21.780 --> 24:22.860
Even if Tian Huo's marriage

24:22.890 --> 24:23.970
is fake,

24:24.260 --> 24:25.540
our Bright Moon Palace

24:25.560 --> 24:26.860
should still have someone to accompany her.

24:27.130 --> 24:28.490
In terms of Human Race,

24:28.890 --> 24:30.090
we'd count as family from the bride's side.

24:32.170 --> 24:32.790
How about this:

24:32.820 --> 24:34.330
I'll go with Bai Shuo to the Emotion Tree,

24:34.360 --> 24:35.680
and you stay with Tian Huo.

24:35.700 --> 24:36.400
Why?

24:38.460 --> 24:39.280
Cang Shan,

24:40.050 --> 24:41.070
come with me.

24:53.050 --> 24:55.250
When did you fall in love with Tian Huo?

24:55.270 --> 24:57.550
You...

24:57.580 --> 24:58.410
How did you...

24:58.430 --> 24:59.750
How did I find it out?

25:00.460 --> 25:01.700
It was on that day

25:01.730 --> 25:03.390
when we talked about your age.

25:05.370 --> 25:07.990
So you don't want to attend the wedding

25:08.090 --> 25:10.750
because you don't want to see Tian Huo marry someone else?

25:12.240 --> 25:15.170
Tian Huo has made it clear to me.

25:17.410 --> 25:18.500
We are

25:19.430 --> 25:20.630
just friends.

25:22.320 --> 25:23.300
Bai Shuo,

25:23.530 --> 25:25.110
why does Mu Jiu

25:25.330 --> 25:26.770
get to be the one she likes,

25:26.790 --> 25:27.590
while I'm

25:28.200 --> 25:29.330
just a friend?

25:30.260 --> 25:31.750
Isn't being a friend good enough?

25:32.520 --> 25:33.580
I don't know.

25:33.790 --> 25:35.060
I just feel uneasy

25:35.080 --> 25:36.750
at the thought of

25:37.850 --> 25:39.460
seeing her marry Mu Jiu.

25:40.050 --> 25:42.280
You've known Tian Huo longer than I have.

25:42.490 --> 25:44.800
What kind of person do you think she is?

25:45.580 --> 25:47.140
She's carefree,

25:48.260 --> 25:49.030
brave,

25:51.190 --> 25:52.360
and also very smart.

25:52.530 --> 25:54.770
She's also sensitive, pessimistic,

25:54.800 --> 25:56.080
and a bit weak at times.

25:56.100 --> 25:57.060
How could you say that?

25:57.090 --> 25:58.680
Those aren't necessarily flaws.

25:59.160 --> 26:01.170
Maybe your master

26:01.190 --> 26:02.670
is just like her.

26:04.910 --> 26:06.910
Tian Huo has been through so much in the past.

26:06.930 --> 26:08.520
It's hard for her to trust anyone again.

26:09.120 --> 26:10.640
You and Fan Yue became friends

26:10.640 --> 26:12.760
only after

26:12.850 --> 26:14.400
going through so many things with her.

26:16.450 --> 26:18.890
Now that Tian Huo has finally managed to tear apart the knots in her heart

26:18.920 --> 26:20.840
and is willing to give things a try with Mu Jiu,

26:20.890 --> 26:22.740
this wedding

26:22.760 --> 26:24.000
is far from simple for her.

26:24.030 --> 26:25.060
But she said

26:25.080 --> 26:26.500
it's just a temporary solution.

26:28.270 --> 26:29.480
You

26:29.600 --> 26:31.000
don't understand her.

26:32.820 --> 26:34.270
Even if it's not about that,

26:35.090 --> 26:36.300
I still find

26:36.660 --> 26:38.160
Chang Mei's treatment of Mu Jiu

26:38.370 --> 26:39.740
quite strange.

26:41.240 --> 26:43.000
If Chang Mei doesn't have any ill intentions tonight,

26:43.000 --> 26:43.920
then fine.

26:43.940 --> 26:45.860
But if she truly has other plans,

26:45.890 --> 26:48.340
we won't allow Tian Huo to marry Mu Jiu.

26:48.360 --> 26:50.000
I have Fan Yue protecting me,

26:50.090 --> 26:52.630
but Tian Huo will have to face the entire Fox Clan alone.

26:52.700 --> 26:54.170
If you stay and help her,

26:54.190 --> 26:55.670
we can rest assured.

26:55.710 --> 26:56.870
So, are we going to

26:57.180 --> 26:58.030
fight again tonight?

26:58.740 --> 26:59.850
I hope not.

27:00.270 --> 27:02.360
No matter what Chang Mei's goal is,

27:02.610 --> 27:04.840
she's just a pitiful person trapped by love.

27:05.440 --> 27:07.920
Maybe she has no choice for many things.

27:08.260 --> 27:10.490
If it really comes to a battle,

27:11.090 --> 27:12.440
no one will come out as the winner.

27:12.840 --> 27:14.460
Isn't the situation with the Fox Clan from back then

27:14.590 --> 27:16.110
the perfect example of this?

27:22.610 --> 27:24.890
It hurts so much!

27:24.920 --> 27:26.890
It hurts so much!

27:26.910 --> 27:27.870
It hurts!

27:27.900 --> 27:29.250
It hurts!

27:29.270 --> 27:29.990
Young Master.

27:30.020 --> 27:30.630
What's wrong with you?

27:30.650 --> 27:32.870
Hurry up. Get me some medicine!

27:32.890 --> 27:33.580
Go.

27:34.340 --> 27:35.990
Hurry up, report to Master Chang.

27:38.650 --> 27:39.450
Young Master.

27:39.540 --> 27:40.770
Are you okay?

27:48.040 --> 27:48.730
Idiot.

27:49.150 --> 27:50.590
Luckily, I have a lot of stocks.

27:55.490 --> 27:57.040
Huo!

27:59.640 --> 28:00.640
You're here.

28:01.820 --> 28:03.150
You scared me.

28:03.170 --> 28:05.130
I thought Auntie and the others...

28:10.980 --> 28:12.070
You're so beautiful.

28:13.420 --> 28:15.030
It suits you so well.

28:15.060 --> 28:16.330
Your hairpin looks great too.

28:16.380 --> 28:17.570
Your makeup is also stunning.

28:19.150 --> 28:20.390
I mean

28:20.410 --> 28:21.900
you're already so beautiful.

28:21.970 --> 28:23.870
Even if you wore a torn sack,

28:23.890 --> 28:25.580
you'd still look like a celestial being descending to the mortal world.

28:29.580 --> 28:30.390
Huo.

28:31.130 --> 28:32.460
Why are you ignoring me?

28:35.390 --> 28:36.080
Huo.

28:44.760 --> 28:45.670
Cursed technique?

28:48.670 --> 28:50.390
Have you forgotten the rules I told you?

28:50.680 --> 28:51.440
Go back.

28:52.300 --> 28:53.460
Auntie, I'm not leaving.

28:53.480 --> 28:54.350
Let me just take a look at her.

28:54.380 --> 28:55.940
Your wedding is tonight.

28:55.960 --> 28:57.770
She still has a lot to prepare.

28:57.800 --> 28:59.610
You can take your time to look at her once the marriage is settled.

28:59.880 --> 29:00.960
She is acting strange.

29:00.980 --> 29:02.510
She's been cursed.

29:04.570 --> 29:05.460
Is that so?

29:07.740 --> 29:09.430
You did this?

29:13.580 --> 29:14.590
There's a curse on the wedding dress.

29:14.590 --> 29:15.350
Do you want to lose your life?

29:15.370 --> 29:16.610
She is my life.

29:16.720 --> 29:18.390
If you insist on harming her today,

29:18.420 --> 29:19.840
then you might as well kill me first.

29:22.740 --> 29:23.710
What did you say?

29:24.120 --> 29:25.120
I said

29:25.140 --> 29:26.970
please kill me first.

29:37.190 --> 29:38.270
Master Chang, we...

29:38.290 --> 29:39.530
Get out!

29:40.740 --> 29:41.540
Yes.

29:43.270 --> 29:44.740
I raised you myself.

29:44.930 --> 29:46.570
In the cold, I feared you might freeze;

29:46.650 --> 29:48.530
when you were sick, I feared you might be in pain.

29:48.770 --> 29:50.940
For all these years, I couldn't bear to let you suffer even the slightest bit of hardship

29:50.960 --> 29:52.360
or injustice.

29:53.690 --> 29:55.100
Yet in the end,

29:55.670 --> 29:58.190
the life I've worked so hard to protect

29:58.210 --> 29:59.590
is being used so carelessly

29:59.610 --> 30:01.480
to protect an outsider.

30:02.490 --> 30:05.120
Do I even matter to you as your auntie?

30:08.830 --> 30:10.230
Auntie, I haven't forgotten the kindness

30:10.260 --> 30:11.500
you've shown me,

30:12.640 --> 30:14.320
but Huo has nothing to do with all of this.

30:14.340 --> 30:15.400
She shouldn't have to bear any of this.

30:15.400 --> 30:17.070
She and Fan Yue came to Jingyou Mountain

30:17.070 --> 30:18.310
just to harm you!

30:18.330 --> 30:19.760
All they want is the Weak Water Stone.

30:19.790 --> 30:21.280
How does that translate into wanting to harm me?

30:21.390 --> 30:22.980
They've never had any hostility toward the Fox Clan.

30:23.090 --> 30:23.750
In the Outlanders' City,

30:23.750 --> 30:25.680
they've protected me time and time again.

30:26.240 --> 30:26.890
Auntie,

30:27.600 --> 30:28.810
I'm begging you,

30:28.840 --> 30:29.970
just give them the Weak Water Stone, alright?

30:30.000 --> 30:30.850
Shut up!

30:31.250 --> 30:33.110
I'll tell you one last time:

30:33.570 --> 30:35.130
not a single word more

30:35.370 --> 30:37.010
about the Weak Water Stone.

30:39.540 --> 30:40.490
Ms. Bai!

30:40.970 --> 30:42.020
Ms. Bai!

30:42.050 --> 30:43.150
Is Master here?

30:46.100 --> 30:46.900
Master.

30:46.930 --> 30:48.100
I've finally found you!

30:48.120 --> 30:48.760
Bad news!

30:48.790 --> 30:49.450
What is it?

30:49.500 --> 30:51.060
Lady Tian Huo is in trouble.

30:51.510 --> 30:52.380
Lady Tian Huo

30:52.410 --> 30:54.200
has been cursed with a very complicated spell.

30:54.230 --> 30:55.780
We tried to break it for her,

30:55.800 --> 30:56.870
but we were met with backlash.

30:56.890 --> 30:58.720
Only a powerful demon with high-level mana

30:58.750 --> 31:00.170
can help her.

31:00.190 --> 31:01.590
Master asked you to go take a look.

31:01.620 --> 31:02.880
Tian Huo got cursed?

31:03.170 --> 31:04.260
Why would she be cursed?

31:04.700 --> 31:05.460
Perhaps

31:05.480 --> 31:07.590
it was those two people from the Cold Spring Palace in the forest who did it.

31:07.620 --> 31:09.420
In any case, with the wedding approaching,

31:09.510 --> 31:11.350
if we don't break the curse soon,

31:11.370 --> 31:12.530
things will become troublesome.

31:13.620 --> 31:14.210
Lead the way.

31:22.100 --> 31:23.100
Ms. Bai.

31:24.760 --> 31:25.910
It's getting late.

31:25.930 --> 31:27.410
May I take you to the Emotion Tree now?

31:28.880 --> 31:30.360
I'll go call Fan Yue to come along.

31:30.390 --> 31:31.320
No need.

31:32.070 --> 31:32.960
To release Qi,

31:32.960 --> 31:34.290
only your blood is needed.

31:34.350 --> 31:35.110
It doesn't matter

31:35.110 --> 31:36.180
whether Master of Bright Moon

31:36.210 --> 31:37.370
goes or not.

31:38.010 --> 31:38.810
Could it be that

31:39.600 --> 31:41.810
the feelings Ms. Bai expressed toward Ling Long

31:41.830 --> 31:42.870
were all fake?

31:43.430 --> 31:44.560
Or is it

31:45.070 --> 31:46.720
because you don't trust me?

31:51.370 --> 31:52.610
You must be joking.

31:52.640 --> 31:53.610
Please.

32:12.400 --> 32:14.680
Here he Comes.

32:21.320 --> 32:22.320
Young Master is here.

32:24.370 --> 32:25.380
Young Master is here.

32:25.400 --> 32:26.420
Young Master is here.

32:29.070 --> 32:30.990
You can save Tian Huo,

32:31.090 --> 32:33.320
but you must do as I say.

32:33.830 --> 32:35.970
Tonight, I will have Elder Chang Sheng

32:35.990 --> 32:38.000
announce that the position of Master will be passed on to you.

32:38.020 --> 32:39.460
If you dare refuse,

32:40.610 --> 32:42.410
I will never spare the life of Tian Huo.

32:43.240 --> 32:44.080
Understand?

32:45.110 --> 32:46.450
I don't understand.

32:46.470 --> 32:47.440
Auntie, why are you

32:47.440 --> 32:49.090
so determined to pass the position to me?

32:49.120 --> 32:50.690
There are some things I'm not telling you now,

32:50.710 --> 32:52.010
but it's for your own good.

32:52.270 --> 32:53.570
After tonight,

32:53.890 --> 32:55.810
I will make sure all those who could harm you

32:55.830 --> 32:56.900
are gone.

32:56.930 --> 32:57.880
At that time,

32:57.900 --> 32:59.280
whether you understand or not,

32:59.490 --> 33:01.530
the promise I made to my sister

33:01.550 --> 33:02.930
will be fulfilled.

33:03.310 --> 33:04.240
Your sister?

33:05.810 --> 33:06.740
Auntie's sister

33:06.760 --> 33:07.950
isn't the Ling Long Saintess?

33:07.980 --> 33:09.490
What did you promise her?

33:09.970 --> 33:10.940
What does it have to do with me?

33:10.970 --> 33:12.240
What do you want?

33:15.970 --> 33:16.850
Auntie,

33:21.720 --> 33:23.350
what's going on?

33:30.160 --> 33:31.930
Master, please act quickly to break the curse.

33:32.100 --> 33:33.420
This curse is extremely powerful,

33:33.440 --> 33:35.120
and if we wait too long, it may be too late.

33:46.550 --> 33:48.200
Tian Huo is a member of Bright Moon Palace.

33:48.790 --> 33:50.030
Why do you seem even more anxious

33:50.030 --> 33:51.360
than me?

33:53.230 --> 33:54.470
You're being too modest.

33:54.500 --> 33:56.540
Lady Tian Huo is about to marry into the Fox Clan,

33:56.560 --> 33:58.070
so she will also be a member of mine.

33:58.100 --> 33:59.710
The wedding in the palace is about to begin,

33:59.730 --> 34:01.080
and if the time comes

34:01.110 --> 34:02.590
and the bride and groom haven't shown up,

34:02.610 --> 34:03.930
it would be quite embarrassing.

34:05.310 --> 34:06.530
I see.

34:07.170 --> 34:08.310
I misunderstood.

34:42.969 --> 34:43.820
What's going on?

34:43.850 --> 34:44.929
Didn't they say it was a wedding?

34:44.949 --> 34:45.980
-Yeah.
-So what is this?

34:46.239 --> 34:47.449
Yeah, it's strange.

34:47.469 --> 34:49.170
What's going on?

34:49.969 --> 34:51.409
Master has issued a decree:

34:51.679 --> 34:53.159
everyone, listen attentively.

34:53.190 --> 34:55.460
A thousand years have passed, and I have grown old

34:55.480 --> 34:58.210
and frail, unable to shoulder the rise and fall of the Fox Clan.

34:58.240 --> 35:00.840
The heavy responsibility entrusted to me weighs on my heart.

35:00.860 --> 35:03.900
After much consideration, I only see the talent of Mu Jiu.

35:04.150 --> 35:05.740
He's talented?

35:06.010 --> 35:07.420
With the governance and nurturing, success has been achieved,

35:07.440 --> 35:08.910
and he is capable of bringing about reform.

35:09.080 --> 35:10.570
I hereby offer this to Heaven and Earth,

35:10.600 --> 35:12.960
and thus the position of Master is granted.

35:14.290 --> 35:15.990
What's wrong with the position?

35:16.010 --> 35:17.930
Yes. It doesn't make any sense.

35:18.030 --> 35:19.150
Yes.

35:20.600 --> 35:22.700
-Can he really become Master?
-Yeah.

35:24.850 --> 35:26.050
I, Elder Chang Sheng,

35:26.070 --> 35:27.110
lead the tribe

35:27.140 --> 35:28.890
to greet the new Master.

35:28.920 --> 35:31.460
Greetings, new Master.

35:32.980 --> 35:33.790
Chang Sheng,

35:34.930 --> 35:36.690
is Chang Mei being reckless

35:36.710 --> 35:38.240
and you're going along with her?

35:38.790 --> 35:40.380
What kind of talent is Mu Jiu?

35:40.410 --> 35:42.300
How could he inherit the position?

35:42.320 --> 35:43.610
Yes, how could he?

35:43.610 --> 35:44.400
How could he?

35:44.420 --> 35:45.610
How could he?

35:45.710 --> 35:46.800
Yeah.

35:46.800 --> 35:48.010
Make it clear!

35:51.420 --> 35:52.300
Elder!

35:53.780 --> 35:55.620
Master has issued another decree:

35:55.960 --> 35:58.390
anyone who disagrees with Mu Jiu inheriting the position

35:58.580 --> 36:00.360
will be killed on the spot.

36:19.590 --> 36:22.110
Actually, time can really change someone.

36:22.130 --> 36:23.220
Right?

36:23.740 --> 36:25.310
Ms. Bai, why do you say that?

36:25.660 --> 36:27.180
Ling Long once said that

36:27.200 --> 36:29.160
Wu has always been carefree

36:29.270 --> 36:30.720
and didn't like practicing spells since she was young,

36:30.970 --> 36:33.820
which is why she hoped she would leave the Fox Clan with Qi.

36:34.030 --> 36:35.680
A vow of eternal love,
a lifetime for one person.

36:37.300 --> 36:38.790
But now, a millennium has passed.

36:38.820 --> 36:40.790
Master, you've become
a figure of immense power,

36:40.820 --> 36:42.110
revered and feared by all.

36:42.200 --> 36:44.520
No one in the Fox Clan dares to defy you.

36:45.060 --> 36:46.350
If Ling Long were still alive

36:46.380 --> 36:47.570
to see this,

36:47.600 --> 36:50.050
she probably wouldn't believe her own eyes.

36:50.640 --> 36:52.330
But if Ling Long were still here,

36:52.440 --> 36:54.210
I wouldn't have become who I am today.

36:54.930 --> 36:56.580
The carefree days of my youth were possible

36:56.610 --> 36:57.280
only because

36:57.280 --> 36:59.420
I had an elder sister
who took care of everything.

37:00.370 --> 37:01.860
Who wouldn't want to remain

37:02.440 --> 37:03.930
a carefree child forever,

37:03.960 --> 37:05.370
sheltered from the storms of life?

37:05.390 --> 37:07.390
Since you understand this,

37:07.420 --> 37:10.170
then why pressure Mu Jiu
to take the role of Master?

37:10.310 --> 37:11.320
Why bring up Mu Jiu

37:11.320 --> 37:12.920
all of a sudden?

37:13.960 --> 37:14.830
All right,

37:15.170 --> 37:16.960
let's talk about Ling Long then.

37:17.020 --> 37:18.750
You love your sister so much

37:18.780 --> 37:20.530
that you gave up freedom and chose to remain

37:20.550 --> 37:21.780
guarding Jingyou Mountain

37:21.800 --> 37:22.910
for her.

37:22.940 --> 37:24.730
When I asked Elder Chang Wu

37:24.750 --> 37:26.060
about the Master's role,

37:26.090 --> 37:28.100
he explained it's a position passed down
in your family for generations.

37:28.430 --> 37:30.150
Even if you have no descendants,

37:30.390 --> 37:32.190
shouldn't the responsibility
to the Fox Clan guide you

37:32.330 --> 37:34.830
to choose a qualified successor

37:35.080 --> 37:37.120
rather than a twenty-year-old orphan

37:37.150 --> 37:38.710
with no family?

37:38.730 --> 37:39.230
Am I wrong?

37:39.250 --> 37:41.290
Ms. Bai, you seem unusually interested
in the private matters

37:41.320 --> 37:42.590
of my Fox Clan.

37:42.610 --> 37:44.610
But we came here today for Qi.

37:45.300 --> 37:46.660
Those old stories

37:46.680 --> 37:48.600
can wait until we've freed him.

37:48.630 --> 37:49.420
Let's go.

37:50.260 --> 37:51.510
Why the rush?

37:51.570 --> 37:53.570
With Fan Yue sent away,

37:53.590 --> 37:54.860
my life is right here

37:54.890 --> 37:56.780
for you to claim.

37:56.800 --> 37:58.200
Let me finish what I have to say first,

37:58.230 --> 37:59.420
and then you can make your move.

37:59.440 --> 38:01.690
Ms. Bai, what exactly are you
trying to get at?

38:02.180 --> 38:03.610
I just want to know

38:04.150 --> 38:05.850
who exactly Mu Jiu is.

38:11.190 --> 38:12.170
Old fox,

38:12.970 --> 38:14.260
I'll ask one more time.

38:15.770 --> 38:18.110
Do you agree to the Young Master taking over

38:18.320 --> 38:19.470
as Master?

38:24.580 --> 38:25.170
Yes, I do.

38:29.160 --> 38:31.200
Does anyone else disagree?

38:32.030 --> 38:33.150
No.

38:33.180 --> 38:34.270
I don't agree.

38:40.440 --> 38:41.530
Cang Shan?

38:42.360 --> 38:43.850
Tonight is a big day for Tian Huo.

38:44.680 --> 38:46.400
Whatever tricks your Fox Clan is playing,

38:46.400 --> 38:47.280
I don't care.

38:47.910 --> 38:50.100
But the wedding of the guardian
of Bright Moon Palace

38:50.780 --> 38:52.650
will not be disrupted.

38:56.530 --> 38:57.710
Mu Jiu is just a child

38:57.710 --> 38:59.190
in his twenties,

38:59.210 --> 39:01.780
an orphan with no family.

39:02.440 --> 39:03.960
My bond with him is purely personal.

39:03.980 --> 39:05.140
Surely that's none of your concern?

39:05.170 --> 39:07.630
There are countless ways
to hide a person's true age.

39:07.650 --> 39:10.170
For instance, sealing their growth

39:10.200 --> 39:12.390
so that even a child
born a thousand years ago

39:12.410 --> 39:13.970
could only start aging

39:14.000 --> 39:15.170
twenty years ago.

39:15.200 --> 39:17.100
For someone of your power,

39:17.150 --> 39:18.800
it would be effortless.

39:18.890 --> 39:20.490
But sometimes, the question
isn't about what you can do.

39:21.080 --> 39:22.140
It's about

39:22.670 --> 39:23.590
why you do it.

39:24.260 --> 39:25.670
Since I discovered

39:25.690 --> 39:27.730
that Mu Jiu is not truly
your biological nephew,

39:27.760 --> 39:29.100
I couldn't stop thinking about it.

39:29.120 --> 39:30.800
The connection between you two

39:30.830 --> 39:32.380
goes far beyond what can be explained

39:32.400 --> 39:33.560
by the absence of a blood bond.

39:33.590 --> 39:34.880
Your care for Mu Jiu

39:34.900 --> 39:37.490
surpasses even what a mother
would show her own child.

39:37.660 --> 39:39.140
What puzzles me most

39:39.170 --> 39:40.810
is why you chose today,

39:40.830 --> 39:42.530
of all days,

39:42.710 --> 39:44.450
to pass down your title to him.

39:48.110 --> 39:49.920
Then I finally remembered.

39:49.780 --> 39:54.780
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

39:50.540 --> 39:52.070
Today, the first day
of the ninth lunar month,

39:52.580 --> 39:53.700
marks a thousand years

39:53.720 --> 39:54.990
since Rong Xian

39:55.020 --> 39:57.190
was ambushed by the Sect Leader of Kunlun,

39:57.210 --> 39:58.600
lost his mind,

39:57.900 --> 40:03.590
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

39:58.630 --> 40:01.030
and annihilated
the entire Fox Clan in one day.

40:01.050 --> 40:02.100
It was also the day

40:02.260 --> 40:03.670
Ling Long died a tragic death.

40:04.000 --> 40:05.320
Is that correct?

40:06.220 --> 40:13.620
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

40:14.540 --> 40:19.730
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

40:14.570 --> 40:17.530
The Contemplation Stone must have
taken us into Rong Xian's realm of resentment.

40:17.560 --> 40:19.040
If my guess is correct,

40:19.220 --> 40:21.650
it was Fan Yue
who defied destiny in that realm,

40:21.810 --> 40:23.760
giving Mu Jiu a chance to live.

40:23.850 --> 40:25.570
The Contemplation Stone's power

40:25.630 --> 40:28.130
then allowed Mu Jiu
to survive in this world.

40:28.290 --> 40:30.300
He is, in fact, Ling Long's child.

40:35.630 --> 40:36.510
Cang Shan,

40:37.020 --> 40:38.140
look carefully.

40:38.160 --> 40:39.650
Lady Tian Huo is not here.

40:39.730 --> 40:42.080
This is a matter concerning
only Jingyou Mountain.

40:42.110 --> 40:43.810
It has nothing to do
with your Bright Moon Palace.

40:43.900 --> 40:45.200
That's not for you to decide.

40:48.080 --> 40:48.870
Mu Jiu,

40:49.970 --> 40:51.890
Tian Huo told me herself

40:52.580 --> 40:53.530
that she likes you.

40:54.890 --> 40:56.060
It might not be much,

40:56.730 --> 40:58.310
and it might just be the beginning,

40:58.490 --> 40:59.360
but

41:00.490 --> 41:02.180
her feelings are real.

41:04.890 --> 41:06.140
Since she likes you,

41:06.740 --> 41:08.580
that makes you the one
who can bring her joy.

41:08.850 --> 41:10.200
But if you become the Master,

41:10.430 --> 41:11.380
who will

41:11.620 --> 41:13.390
bring her happiness in the future?

41:14.590 --> 41:15.500
That's why

41:16.150 --> 41:17.790
I'm against it.

41:20.970 --> 41:22.560
Fox Clan, heed my command!

41:22.690 --> 41:24.120
Arrest him!

41:27.260 --> 41:28.360
Young Master.

41:29.610 --> 41:30.680
Everyone, back off!

41:30.880 --> 41:31.630
Cang Shan,

41:31.980 --> 41:33.020
drop the knife.

41:33.050 --> 41:34.370
- You...
- What?

41:34.400 --> 41:35.560
If anything happens to you,

41:35.810 --> 41:37.240
Huo will have my head for this.

41:38.210 --> 41:39.280
Get out of the way!

41:39.300 --> 41:40.540
All of you, stand back!

41:41.510 --> 41:43.870
You're afraid that the resentment
and curses that once fell upon Ling Long

41:43.900 --> 41:45.070
will now land on Mu Jiu.

41:45.180 --> 41:47.620
That's why you've gone to
such lengths to hide this secret,

41:47.640 --> 41:48.900
even using unknown means

41:48.930 --> 41:50.040
to alter his age

41:50.070 --> 41:50.840
and his background.

41:50.840 --> 41:51.760
Today, of all days, was chosen

41:51.760 --> 41:53.800
because it's Ling Long's death anniversary.

41:53.800 --> 41:54.840
You want her to see

41:54.840 --> 41:56.320
that Mu Jiu has grown into a man

41:56.350 --> 41:57.830
and to give her back everything

41:57.880 --> 41:58.710
that should have been hers.

41:58.710 --> 41:59.480
Enough!

42:04.800 --> 42:07.910
Ms. Bai, you're indeed incredibly smart.

42:08.410 --> 42:09.810
You're right.

42:10.370 --> 42:13.060
Both you and the Master of Bright Moon
have shown kindness to Mu Jiu.

42:13.090 --> 42:14.050
By all rights,

42:14.520 --> 42:16.670
I shouldn't treat you this way.

42:16.850 --> 42:18.400
But I've gone to great lengths

42:18.440 --> 42:20.320
to protect Jiu's secret for so long.

42:20.870 --> 42:23.110
I can't let anyone uncover it now.

42:24.240 --> 42:25.510
Your kindness…

42:25.530 --> 42:27.890
I'll repay it in my next life.

42:46.250 --> 42:47.570
They won't dare lay a finger on me.

42:48.030 --> 42:48.930
Go find Huo right now!

42:48.950 --> 42:50.170
My aunt intends to harm her.

42:50.190 --> 42:51.200
You must save her.

42:51.220 --> 42:52.270
Do you hear me?

42:53.650 --> 42:54.710
Master said

42:54.730 --> 42:56.220
the strong should stay behind
to hold the line.

42:56.250 --> 42:57.360
You go find Tian Huo.

42:57.380 --> 42:58.570
If anything happens to her,

42:58.680 --> 42:59.810
you'll pay for it.

43:00.330 --> 43:00.770
Now, go!

43:01.750 --> 43:02.620
Stop Young Master!

43:02.710 --> 43:03.590
Don't let him get away!

43:03.590 --> 43:04.480
- Yes.
- Yes.

43:16.340 --> 43:17.330
Who would've thought?

43:17.360 --> 43:18.680
Before we could act,

43:18.700 --> 43:20.620
the Fox Clan is already falling apart.

43:21.260 --> 43:24.220
By now, Bai Shuo should have been taken
to the Emotion Tree by Chang Mei.

43:24.420 --> 43:25.140
Let's move.

43:28.260 --> 43:28.970
Chong Zhao,

43:28.990 --> 43:30.210
what are you doing?

43:30.530 --> 43:31.930
Master wants Bai Shuo

43:31.960 --> 43:33.120
for the power of the Contemplation Stone

43:33.140 --> 43:34.490
to become the strongest among demons.

43:34.670 --> 43:35.870
But if

43:35.890 --> 43:37.840
Chang Mei and Fan Yue die tonight,

43:37.930 --> 43:39.330
she'll already be unmatched

43:39.360 --> 43:40.880
and won't need Bai Shuo anymore.

43:40.900 --> 43:42.060
Are you out of your mind?

43:42.090 --> 43:44.370
How could the two of us
possibly kill Fan Yue and Chang Mei?

43:44.890 --> 43:45.880
It won't be "us."

43:45.900 --> 43:47.130
Just me.

44:00.220 --> 44:01.100
Chong Zhao,

44:01.230 --> 44:02.420
you are injured.

44:02.570 --> 44:04.530
Going alone is suicide!

44:04.560 --> 44:06.810
I brought some of Chen Ye's evil insects
when I came here.

44:06.830 --> 44:07.980
They're not fully refined yet,

44:08.010 --> 44:09.810
but they've absorbed enough
celestial and demonic energy to be effective.

44:09.840 --> 44:10.850
Don't worry.

44:11.200 --> 44:12.440
You will be safe.

44:13.580 --> 44:14.370
Chong Zhao!

44:15.070 --> 44:16.160
I can help you.

44:19.590 --> 44:20.460
No need.

44:21.170 --> 44:22.230
Our paths were never the same,

44:22.530 --> 44:23.900
so we were never meant
to walk them together.

44:24.210 --> 44:25.840
Tomorrow, you'll be free
to leave this place.

44:26.210 --> 44:27.450
Are you worried about me?

44:27.980 --> 44:29.910
You're afraid Grand Master
will punish me if he finds out,

44:30.120 --> 44:30.890
aren't you?

44:41.520 --> 44:42.370
Chong...
